data.description: Sellers are offering $5000 CREDIT to the buyers at closing! Use the credit to buy down the interest rate, use towards updates or closing costs.  Bayberry Farms has something for everyone!   Enjoy spending your time at the neighborhood pool, basketball court, tennis courts, open space for soccer/football/baseball, 2 neighborhood playgrounds and access to the 15 Mile, paved, Kent Trails.  This 3100+ sq ft home has newer vinyl plank flooring, newer carpet, family room with gas fireplace, flex space (2nd living room or home office), newer LG appliances, and slider to a spacious stamped concrete patio perfect for entertaining friends and family in the private back yard!   Upstairs you will find an oversized primary suite with dual sinks, soaking tub, separate water closet with stand up shower and large walk in closet. Three additional spacious bedrooms and another full bath complete the second story. The lower level is partially finished with a built in bar, rec room, game room, New Furnace (12/2022) and tons of storage.  Extra parking pad to the side of the driveway, storage shed, and so much more!  This home is a Must See!
